{"type":null,"faqId":47126,"title":"zero手环如何与手机解除绑定？ios如何忽略设备（手环）？","answer":"<p>\n<p style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; BACKGROUND: white; MARGIN-LEFT: 0cm; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; MARGIN-RIGHT: 0cm\"><span style=\"COLOR: black\">您好，手环收手机接触绑定，请按照以下步骤操作：</span></p>\n<p style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; BACKGROUND: white; MARGIN-LEFT: 0cm; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; MARGIN-RIGHT: 0cm; WORD-SPACING: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\"><span style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 'Times New Roman','serif'; COLOR: black\">1</span><span style=\"COLOR: black\">、</span><span style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 'Times New Roman','serif'; COLOR: black\">Android</span><span style=\"COLOR: black\">用户</span></p>\n<p style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; BACKGROUND: white; MARGIN-LEFT: 0cm; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; MARGIN-RIGHT: 0cm; WORD-SPACING: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\"><span style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 'Times New Roman','serif'; COLOR: black\">(1)</span><span style=\"COLOR: black\">请打开</span><span style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 'Times New Roman','serif'; COLOR: black\">APP</span><span style=\"COLOR: black\">，点击左上角手环图标进入到设置界面，点击界面最下方的</span><span style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 'Times New Roman','serif'; COLOR: black\">“</span><span style=\"COLOR: black\">解除绑定</span><span style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 'Times New Roman','serif'; COLOR: black\">”</span><span style=\"COLOR: black\">按钮。</span></p>\n<p style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; BACKGROUND: white; MARGIN-LEFT: 0cm; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; MARGIN-RIGHT: 0cm; WORD-SPACING: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\"><span style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 'Times New Roman','serif'; COLOR: black\"><img border=\"0\" alt=\"http://w3.huawei.com/tkbmng/ha-i/74267_sj0mb.png\" width=\"189\" height=\"320\" src=\"http://consumer.huawei.com/support/servlet/imageServlet?dlType=SupportImage&imagePath=/20151016150955137001.gif\"></span></p>\n<p style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; BACKGROUND: white; MARGIN-LEFT: 0cm; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; MARGIN-RIGHT: 0cm; WORD-SPACING: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\"><span style=\"COLOR: black\">（</span><span style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 'Times New Roman','serif'; CO